Interface MergeSortedIterator.Equivalence<E>

  • Enclosing class:
    MergeSortedIterator<E>

    public static interface MergeSortedIterator.Equivalence<E>
    Defines how elements of type 'E' are related to each other. Unlike a simple comparator, two items can be "independent" and have precedence operations.
